<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{% block title %}{{ title }} - 详情页{% endblock %}</title>
  {% block head %}
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/tpl_static/css/output.css">
  {% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
  {% block header %}
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">首页</a>
        <a href="/detail">详情页</a>
        <a href="/category">分类页</a>
        <a href="/agreement">协议页</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  {% endblock %}

  <main class="main-content">
    {% block content %}
<div class="container">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>详情页模板</h1>
    <p class="page-info">页面类型: {{ pageType }} | 模板名称: {{ templateName }}</p>
  </div>
  
  <article class="detail-content">
    <h2>详情页标题</h2>
    <div class="meta-info">
      <span class="date">发布时间: 2024-01-01</span>
      <span class="author">作者: Admin</span>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content-body">
      <p>这是详情页的内容区域，用于展示详细信息。</p>
      <p>你可以在这里添加文章内容、产品详情等。</p>
    </div>
  </article>

</div>
{% endblock %}
  </main>

  {% block footer %}
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2024 All rights reserved</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
  {% endblock %}

  {% block scripts %}
  <script src="/static/js/common.js"></script>
  {% endblock %}
</body>
</html>